      ],
      "source": "https://mainstreetzephyrhills.org/our-history/"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "The Zephyrhills Public Library, founded in 1912, joined the Pasco County Library Cooperative and got a new building in 2014.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        3,
        13,
