      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zephyrhills%2C_Florida"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "Zephyrhills’ name reflects its rolling topography, with “Zephyr” meaning a gentle west wind and “hills” describing the landscape.",
